rom the unique and distinctive shape of the <a href="/products/stabilo-boss-original-highlighter" class="">STABILO BOSS ORIGINAL highlighters</a>, to the high-quality design of STABILO pens like the point 88, their much sought-after products provide a splash of colour to our everyday lives.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675767368661" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675767368661" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767368623" data-id="1675767368623" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767519795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767519795" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/stabilo-boss-original-highlighter" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/c2ace832-8172-4afc-a431-39d90df1faef/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Medium%20rectangles.%20780px%20x%20500px%20-%20Highlighting.jpg" alt="STABILO BOSS ORIGINAL" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="780" height="500" natural-width="780" natural-height="500" style="" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770662767" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770662767"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="/products/stabilo-boss-original-highlighter" class="">STABILO BOSS ORIGINAL</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770760680" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770760680"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>The STABILO BOSS ORIGINAL highlighter is a popular choice for highlighting important information in text allowing you to focus on what matters to you since 1971. It's instantly recognisable for its unique shape and its 4-hour cap off time and comfortable grip, and 30 nature, pastel and fluorescent colours.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Why not #HighlightWhatMatters to you and be a part of the </span><a href="https://www.stabilo.com/uk/highlightwhatmatters/" class="" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">STABILO BOSS ORIGINAL campaign.</a></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767384572" data-id="1675767384572" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767638977" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767638977" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/stabilo-woody" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/8009cb54-703b-4398-9bda-df33b22cb5bc/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Medium%20rectangles.%20780px%20x%20500px%20-%20Art%20and%20graphics.jpg" alt="STABILO Hand Lettering" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="780" height="500" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="780" natural-height="500" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770684406" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770684406"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Art & Hand Lettering</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770879686" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770879686"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>If you have a passion for art or simply enjoy drawing, you'll be pleased to know that STABILO has a range of colouring products designed to elevate your creativity and produce exceptional results.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Whether you're an aspiring artist or simply enjoy doodling in your spare time, we have you covered. With a variety of options to choose from, you can explore your artistic side and produce works that are truly remarkable.</span></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1679581028534" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1679581028534" data-layout-lg="3+3+3+3" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+3+3+3" data-layout-sm="6+6+6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12+12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1679580858851" data-id="1679580858851"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679581031253" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1679581031253" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/col